Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Real Estate
Sub-Industry: REIT
Moody National REIT I, Inc. is a real estate investment trust. The Trust acquires a diversified portfolio of real estate investments, including commercial properties, real estate securities and debt-related investments.




