Overview
The Direxion Daily MSCI Real Estate Bull andÂ Bear 3X Shares seek daily investment results, before fees and expenses, of 300%, or 300% of the inverse (or opposite), ofÂ the performance of the MSCI US REIT Index. There is no guarantee the funds will meet their stated investment objective.
These leveraged ETFs seek a return that is 300% or -300% of the return ofÂ their benchmark index for a single day. The funds should not be expected to provide three times or negative three timesÂ the return of the benchmarkâs cumulative return for periods greater than a day.

